title: Hafnia Bar
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Catering, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Start with a vegan and gluten-free base then add your fillings/toppings for sandwiches, salads, grain bowls. Meat served is fish and poultry. Has fresh pressed juices, almond milk shakes, acai bowls, raw cakes, coffee, tea.
